Nigerians on social media have reacted to the post of the popular Nollywood actress, Mercy Aigbe revealing her lover, Kazim Adeoti who is alleged to be married. The actress posted the filmmaker’s picture on Sunday via her Instagram page, addressing him as her lover and wishing him a happy birthday. She wrote, “It’s my Boo’s birthday in a bit. @kazimadeoti thank you for being amazing” Mercy Aigbe’s Ex-husband Hails His New Wife Fatherhood Is Beyond Impregnating A Woman-Mercy Aigbe Slams Her… However, most Nigerians expressed their disappointment about her relationship on Instagram, as they claimed she left a cheating husband to date a married man. @_ololade_xx wrote, “You left ur husband to become a second wife…Mercy no get mercy.” @ofure_filmrant wrote, “How do you leave your 411, husband to go and marry another person’s husband? These yeyebrities no wan get sense? Mtchewwww” @sammy.6.9 wrote, “I think say na person husband be this?” @emerie chris wrote, “Lol you see those so called classy ladies, just pray ur husband doesn’t meet them cause my sister they go share am with u shamelessly it is well.” POLL @berry.queen wrote, “Is this not somebody’s husband?” @nurse_canazy wrote, “Yoruba actresses and dating, abi marrying married men ehn….Jesus”